The two other components of the objective function take the knowledge graph into account. One addition considers a link-based measure estimated from the knowledge graph (i.e., Wikipedia). This measure captures the relatedness between entities in the knowledge base, based on the similarity between their incoming links:2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
