The last addition to the objective function places similar entities and words near each other by considering the context of the anchor text. The intuition is the same as in classic Word2Vec, but here, words in the vicinity of the anchor text have to predict the entity mention. Considering a knowledge graph with anchors A and an entity e the goal is to predict context words of the entity:3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
